}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "1246-01000106-50Z" is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
The FCC manual states the default SSID patterns are '''WL-330NUL-private-XXXX''' :and '''WL-330NUL-Guest-XXXX''' when in router mode.
The default SSID pattern appears to be '''WL-330NUL-Private-XXXX''', where :'''XXXX''' is the last two octets of the BSSID (lower case letters). The default guest network SSID looks to be '''WL-330NUL-Guest-XXXX'''.. :but it does not seem to be enabled by default.
The power adapter (USB Female-A) shown is a '''Ktec''' :KSAS0060500100VUU ''(100~240VAC ~50/60Hz, 0.18A -> 5VDC, 1A)''.
